WEBVTT

00:01:57.760 --> 00:02:03.456
except for flashes
of pain, grief and anger

00:02:03.480 --> 00:02:05.336
triggered by the news,

00:02:05.360 --> 00:02:07.816
or an insensitive comment,

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:09.080
or just silence.

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:19.736
Marjory Stoneman Douglas High School
lost 17 precious lives

00:02:19.760 --> 00:02:21.360
on that horrible day.

